                    "description": "\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tDataset Summary\n\t\n\nRedPajama-Instruct-Data is curated from a diverse collection of NLP tasks from both P3 (BigScience) and Natural Instruction (AI2), \nand conduct aggressive decontamination against HELM, \nin two steps: (1) We first conduct semantic search using each validation example in HELM as the query and get top-100 similar instances from the Instruct data set and check tasks that have any returned instances overlapping (using 10-Gram) with the validation example. \nWe remove the\u2026 See the full description on the dataset page: https://huggingface.co/datasets/togethercomputer/RedPajama-Data-Instruct.",
